    <item>
      <title>JavaScript Async/Await - Xử lý bất đồng bộ</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/javascript-async-await/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/javascript-async-await/</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;asyncawait-trong-javascript&#34;&gt;Async/Await trong JavaScript&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Async/Await là cách hiện đại để xử lý bất đồng bộ trong JavaScript, làm cho code dễ đọc hơn.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;so-sánh-callback-promise-và-asyncawait&#34;&gt;So sánh Callback, Promise, và Async/Await&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;callback-hell&#34;&gt;Callback Hell&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;fetchUser(id, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(user) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    fetchPosts(user.id, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(posts) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        fetchComments(posts[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bd93f9&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;].id, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt;(comments) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            console.log(comments);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;promise-chain&#34;&gt;Promise Chain&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;fetchUser(id)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    .then(user =&amp;gt; fetchPosts(user.id))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    .then(posts =&amp;gt; fetchComments(posts[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bd93f9&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;].id))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    .then(comments =&amp;gt; console.log(comments))
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    .&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt;(error =&amp;gt; console.error(error));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;asyncawait&#34;&gt;Async/Await&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8be9fd;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; getComments(id) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; user &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; fetchUser(id);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; posts &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; fetchPosts(user.id);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; comments &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; fetchComments(posts[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bd93f9&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;].id);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        console.log(comments);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    } &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ff79c6&#34;&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (error) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        console.error(error);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Async/Await làm code trông giống như synchronous nhưng thực tế là bất đồng bộ.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
